    "body": "@mcdee Thanks for bringing these up! \r\n\r\nI've raised a pull request to resolve the genesis state issue.  I believe the issue with the `previous_justified_checkpoint` equaling the `current_justified_checkpoint` is due to the finality issues on Medalla. In [this](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#justification-and-finalization) portion of the eth2 spec, the `previous_justified_checkpoint` is updated to the `current_justified_checkpoint` before checking for participation.",
